data.description: This impressive 5-bedroom 3.5-bath home situated in the highly sought-after Wildhorse community awaits new home owners. This home is nestled in a cul-de-sac and set on a spacious .44-acre lot with green space offering you endless opportunities! As you step inside, you're greeted by a formal dining room and a spacious living room with a cozy fireplace, perfect for hosting gatherings or enjoying quality family time. The eat-in kitchen is both practical and spacious, offering an ideal spot for casual dining and gathering. The kitchen boast plenty of cabinets, granite countertops, and a large walk in pantry. The primary bedroom is located downstairs for added convenience and features a beautiful bay window, luxurious walk-in shower, a soaker tub, and double vanity. Upstairs, you'll find four additional generous size bedrooms with walk-in closets, including a convenient Jack and Jill restroom and a secondary bathroom. The large game room offers endless possibilities for entertainment and recreation. With its blend of style, functionality, and ample space, this home is perfect for those seeking comfort and a vibrant community atmosphere. The Wildhorse community offers an abundance of outdoor entertaining with 2 playgrounds, 2 community pools, basketball court, walking/jogging trails, dog park, and is walking distance to the elementary school and daycare center. Minutes from Lackland Air Force Base, La Cantera, The Rim, and major highways. Come see this house today, and call it home tomorrow!
